OL,3,CHouseholds in Hirwaun advised to move
OL,4,Cout of their homes due to RAAC risk
OL,6,FA housing association in Wales has
OL,7,Fadvised 40 households to immediately
OL,8,Fmove out of their homes due to a risk
OL,9,Fof Raac (Reinforced Autoclaved Aerated
OL,10,FConcrete).
OL,12,FSurvey work carried out by Trivallis
OL,13,Fhousing association on its properties
OL,14,Fin the Hirwaun area has identified
OL,15,Fissues with the roofs and ceilings
OL,16,Fconnected to Raac in the building.
OL,18,FRaac is a lightweight form of concrete
OL,19,Fand the way it is created makes it
OL,20,Fweaker than the normal building
OL,21,Fmaterial.
