OL,3,CHouseholds in Hirwaun advised to move
OL,4,Cout of their homes due to RAAC risk
OL,6,FTrivallis has said that it puts tenant
OL,7,Fsafety as the "highest priority" and
OL,8,Fadvised everyone affected to move out
OL,9,Fof their homes immediately.
OL,11,FIt added that it is finding temporary
OL,12,Faccommodation for tenants to stay in
OL,13,Fwhile it surveys their homes and plans
OL,14,Fwhat needs to be done to ensure they
OL,15,Fare safe.
OL,17,FChief Executive Duncan Forbes said:
OL,18,F"We understand that this is
OL,19,Ffrightening and disruptive to those
OL,20,Faffected, but their safety is our main
OL,21,Fconcern.
