OL,3,CHouseholds in Hirwaun advised to move
OL,4,Cout of their homes due to RAAC risk
OL,6,F"We have a zero tolerance for risks to
OL,7,Ftenant safety which is why we are
OL,8,Fadvising people to move out of their
OL,9,Fhomes as quickly as possible.
OL,11,F"Trivallis fully understands the
OL,12,Fgravity of the situation and the
OL,13,Fimpact it has on residents. It is
OL,14,Fdedicated to addressing the immediate
OL,15,Fneeds of those affected.
OL,17,F"We appreciate the understanding and
OL,18,Fco-operation of our residents and the
OL,19,Fcommunity during this challenging
OL,20,Ftime."
